<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- kẖdmtnạ dy fy ạ̹ydk ạ̹tnạzl ạ̹lynạ
 ạ̹mnḥnạ tʿḍydk wạmsk bạ̹ydynạ
 1- ạ̹ḥnạ hnạ fy gẖrbẗ wạ̹nt ạlwṭn lynạ
 wạlgẖrbẗ dy krbẗ ftʿạl ʿzynạ
 mhmạ nḥạwl nʿml ạlḍʿf mạlynạ
 wạlkẖdmẗ rạḥ tkml bqwtk fynạ
 2- ạlkẖdmẗ dy btạʿtk ạ̉rjwk tqwynạ
 wạ̹n knạ bnwạʿdk fạ̹nt ạlʿạml fynạ
 wlạ̉nnạ sẖʿbk bmḥbtk lynạ
 lạzm hạnkẖḍʿ lk tkml bqwtk fynạ
 3- ạlkẖdmẗ dy lmjdk wạ̹ḥnạ hnạ wlạdk
 wạlnạs btsẖtạq lk fạ̉ẓhr lhạ dẖạtk
 ạ̉dwạt wtjhyzạt wạlḥrb jbạrẗ
 wạlʿdw fy mḥạwlạt mạkrẗ wgẖdạrẗ</lyrics>
<title>kẖdmtnạ dy fy ạ̹ydk</title>
</song>